Slingshot
===============================

There is a package for Slingshot in elementary Daily PPA:
$ sudo apt-add-repository ppa:elementary-os/daily
$ sudo apt-get update
$ sudo apt-get install slingshot-launcher

This package is automatically updated everyday.

===============================

You can also compile Slingshot from source.
You need the following dependencies (on Ubuntu/Debian):
- cmake
- libclutter-1.0-dev
- libclutter-gtk-1.0-dev
- libgee-dev
- libgnome-menu-dev
- libgranite-dev
- libgtk-3-dev
- libunity-dev
- libwnck-3-dev
- libzeitgeist-dev
- pkg-config
- valac-0.16 | valac (>= 0.16)
then:
$ mkdir build
$ cd build/
$ cmake .. -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr
$ make
$ sudo make install

===============================

